data.description: ****Seller offering 10k for buyers closing costs****Welcome to this stunning home boasting an expansive 2800 square feet of living space for luxurious living in a neighborhood with only 28 homes. The updated kitchen features beautiful quartz countertops, farmhouse sink, and modern appliances. The master bathroom is a true oasis, complete with a large double shower and double vanity. The large game room upstairs is a fantastic addition, providing the perfect space for game nights, family gatherings, or home theater setup. Fresh interior paint, water softener, roof 2020, water heaters 2023, HVAC 2022, fence 2023.
